# @param {Integer[]} nums
# @return {Integer}
def special_perm(nums)
  mod = 10**9 + 7
  n = nums.size
  dp = Array.new(1 << n, 0)
  dp[0] = 1

  nums.sort!
  
  (1...(1 << n)).each do |mask|
    nums.each_with_index do |num, i|
      next if (mask & (1 << i)).zero?
      prev_mask = mask ^ (1 << i)
      next if dp[prev_mask].zero?
      
      valid = true if prev_mask == 0 # First number in the sequence
      
      nums.each_with_index do |prev_num, j|
        next if (prev_mask & (1 << j)).zero?
        if num % prev_num == 0 || prev_num % num == 0
          dp[mask] = (dp[mask] + dp[prev_mask]) % mod
          break
        end
      end
    end
  end

  dp.last
end
